alt and freshly ground black pepper.","To serve, place the spinach in the centre of a warm plate. Place the duck breast on top of the spinach, arrange the sautéed potatoes around the plate and spoon over the chutney."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_honeyroastduckwithsa_80925","title":"Honey-roast duck with sautéed potatoes, chilli spinach and plum chutney","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":60},"serves":"Serves 1","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
