esian-style fried rice)","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"less than 10 mins","cookingMins":10,"totalMins":40},"serves":"Serves 2","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
