 potatoes and txistorra on top. Drizzle with a little olive oil and garnish with the artichokes."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_octopus_mojo_verde_00254","title":"Octopus, mojo verde, potatoes, artichokes and txistorra","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"1 to 2 hours","cookingMins":120,"totalMins":150},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
