 oven and bake for 25 minutes.","Serve immediately with basmati rice."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_ovenkimurghichickenb_76546","title":"Oven ki murghi (chicken baked with green chillies and onions)","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":60},"serves":"Serves 4-6","image":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_448/recipes/ovenkimurghichickenb_76546_16x9.jpg","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
